These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-1::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: orange, blue, aquamarine, purple, green, ivory, grey
There are 7 different nationalities: brazilian, french, indonesian, italian, nigerian, spanish, thai
 1. the thai is the person who likes purple##1
 2. the brazilian is not to the left of the person who likes aquamarine##8
 3. the brazilian is not to the left of the french##8
 4. the french is somewhere to the left of the person who likes blue##5
 5. the person who likes orange is not to the left of the spanish##8
 6. the person who likes orange is not the french##6
 7. the person who likes green is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who likes green is not to the left of the person who likes grey##8
 9. the nigerian is somewhere between the thai and the french##7
10. the french is the person who likes ivory##1
11. the person who likes ivory is in an odd position##4
12. the spanish is on the right of the thai##1
13. the brazilian is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
14. the person who likes grey is somewhere between the nigerian and the brazilian##7
15. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the brazilian##1
16. the spanish is not to the left of the person who likes green##8
17. the thai is somewhere to the left of the person who likes orange##5
18. the person who likes grey is the indonesian##1
19. the nigerian is on the left or right of the thai##3
20. the person who likes purple is not the spanish##6
21. the person who likes orange is not to the right of the person who likes orange##8
22. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the person who likes green##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |      3       |    4    |    5     |      6      |    7    |
| Color           | ivory | aquamarine | grey | blue  | green  | purple | orange    |
| Nationality   | french   | brazilian   | indonesian   | italian | nigerian | thai        | spanish |

