.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-2::.
There are 7 different nationalities: russian, egyptian, american, pakistani, brazilian, chinese, british
7 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, frog, goat, hamster, horse, lizard
 1. the owner of the hamster is in the middle##1
 2. the owner of the horse is not the american##6
 3. the owner of the frog is not to the left of the owner of the cat##8
 4. the owner of the horse is between the owner of the cat and the american##2
 5. the brazilian is in an odd position##4
 6. the russian is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 7. the british is in an odd position##4
 8. the owner of the frog is not to the left of the owner of the goat##8
 9. the chinese is somewhere to the right of the pakistani##5
10. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
11. the russian is on the right of the brazilian##1
12. the owner of the chinchilla is not to the right of the owner of the goat##8
13. the pakistani is not to the left of the british##8
14. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5
15. the egyptian is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
16. the american is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |      6      |      7      |
| Nationality   | british | pakistani | american    | egyptian | brazilian | russian | chinese |
| Pet     | cat     | horse   | chinchilla | hamster | goat       | frog        | lizard      |

