.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-3::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: blue, light-blue, fuchsia, lilac, ivory, grey, coral
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, golf, lacrosse, parkour, rugby, snowboarding
 1. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
 2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the left of the person who likes light-blue##8
 3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
 4. the person who likes grey is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 6. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
 7. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere to the left of the person who likes fuchsia##5
 8. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
 9. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in the middle##1
10. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the left of the person who likes light-blue##5
11. the person who likes ivory is in an even position##4
12. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who's sport is golf##2
13. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not the person who likes blue##6
14. the person who likes ivory is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4     |      5       |      6      |    7    |
| Color   | lilac       | ivory  | light-blue | coral  | blue  | grey | fuchsia  |
| Sport         | badminton | basketball | golf  | lacrosse | snowboarding | rugby       | parkour |

