 4. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
 5. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the architect##3
 6. the person eating pineapple is the paramedic##1
 7. the dancer is on the far right##1
 8. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the architect##5
 9. the person eating papaya is not to the left of the paramedic##8
10. the dancer is somewhere to the right of the nurse##5
11. the dancer is on the left or right of the scientist##3
12. the scientist is not to the right of the person eating pepper##8
13. the dancer is the person eating pepper##1
14. the person eating asparagus is somewhere to the left of the person eating papaya##5
15. the nurse is somewhere to the left of the architect##5
16. the person eating onion is in the middle##1
17. the scientist is not the person eating papaya##6
18. the nurse is in an even position##4
19. the architect is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
