 7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
 8. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
 9. the owner of the horse is between the person who's birthday is in december and the owner of the rat##2
10. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##5
11. the person who's birthday is in august is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##8
12. the owner of the cat is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##8
13. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##8
