.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-15::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  accountant, architect, dancer, mechanic, musician, pilot, police-officer
There 7 different types of food: papaya, broccoli, pepper, grapefruit, banana, apple, lettuce
 1. the person eating apple is not the musician##6
 2. the mechanic is not the person eating grapefruit##6
 3. the person eating lettuce is not to the right of the police-officer##8
 4. the pilot is on the left or right of the architect##3
 5. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
 6. the accountant is somewhere to the left of the person eating pepper##5
 7. the person eating papaya is somewhere between the person eating broccoli and the person eating banana##7
 8. the pilot is in an odd position##4
 9. the person eating papaya is not the musician##6
10. the person eating lettuce is somewhere to the left of the architect##5
11. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the mechanic##1
12. the architect is on the right of the accountant##1
13. the dancer is somewhere between the person eating apple and the person eating banana##7
14. the musician is in the middle##1
15. the person eating lettuce is not to the right of the police-officer##8
16. the mechanic is not to the left of the person eating lettuce##8
17. the architect is not the person eating papaya##6
18. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person eating banana##1
19. the person eating banana is somewhere to the left of the accountant##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |   3    |    4     |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Job           | police-officer | mechanic | dancer | musician | accountant | architect | pilot |
| Food   | lettuce           | apple  | grapefruit   | banana   | papaya  | pepper   | broccoli |

