.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-16::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: sailing, lacrosse, rowing, rugby, biathlon, cricket, parkour
There are 7 different nationalities: argentine, australian, british, canadian, indonesian, italian, russian
 1. the italian is on the right of the argentine##1
 2. the italian is not to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##8
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the indonesian##1
 4. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
 5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the canadian##3
 6. the australian is on the left of the argentine##1
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is cricket##5
 8. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the left of the russian##5
 9. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##5
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the argentine and the russian##2
11. the canadian is on the left of the indonesian##1
12. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
13. the canadian is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##5
14. the person who's sport is parkour is not the italian##6
15. the argentine is somewhere to the right of the australian##5
16. the argentine is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
17. the person who's sport is parkour is not to the right of the person who's sport is cricket##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |     4      |     5     |    6    |      7      |
| Sport          | parkour | rugby | lacrosse     | sailing  | cricket     | biathlon   | rowing |
| Nationality   | british  | canadian | indonesian | australian | argentine | italian | russian     |

