.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-17::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, siglo, montecristo, dannemann, pall-mall, vegafina, bolivar
There are 7 different nationalities: chinese, colombian, german, japanese, russian, thai, turkish
 1. the colombian is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
 2. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the left of the russian##5
 3. the chinese is not to the right of the bolivar-smoker##8
 4. the japanese is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
 5. the colombian is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3
 6. the pall-mall-smoker is the thai##1
 7. the montecristo-smoker is not to the right of the russian##8
 8. the bolivar-smoker is in an odd position##4
 9. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3
10. the montecristo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the alhambra-smoker##5
11. the thai is on the left of the russian##1
12. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the thai##1
13. the siglo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the dannemann-smoker##5
14. the japanese is somewhere to the left of the pall-mall-smoker##5
15. the turkish is on the left or right of the chinese##3
16. the japanese is not the pall-mall-smoker##6
17. the japanese is the alhambra-smoker##1
18. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the chinese##1
19. the thai is somewhere to the left of the russian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |      5      |     6     |      7      |
| Cigar         | alhambra   | montecristo | bolivar | pall-mall | dannemann | siglo   | vegafina |
| Nationality   | japanese | turkish | chinese     | thai      | russian     | colombian | german      |

