.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-18::.
There 7 different types of food: apple, artichoke, garlic, kale, orange, pomegranate, strawberry
City: san-francisco, london, new-york, paris, hannover, colone, rome
 1. the person traveling to paris is the person eating apple##1
 2. the person eating garlic is not the person traveling to new-york##6
 3. the person eating strawberry is not to the left of the person traveling to rome##8
 4. the person traveling to paris is in the middle##1
 5. the person eating artichoke is somewhere between the person eating garlic and the person traveling to colone##7
 6. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york##3
 7. the person traveling to rome is the person traveling to rome##1
 8. the person eating kale is the person eating kale##1
 9. the person traveling to hannover is not to the right of the person traveling to colone##8
10. the person traveling to san-francisco is not to the left of the person eating garlic##8
11. the person eating orange is not to the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##8
12. the person traveling to colone is on the far right##1
13. the person traveling to london is on the far left or far right##3
14. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3
15. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person eating orange##1
16. the person traveling to rome is not to the right of the person traveling to new-york##8
17. the person eating kale is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
18. the person eating kale is not the person traveling to new-york##6
19. the person traveling to colone is not the person eating artichoke##6
20. the person traveling to colone is in an odd position##4
21. the person eating garlic is in an odd position##4
22. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3
23. the person eating pomegranate is not to the left of the person traveling to rome##8
24. the person eating kale is somewhere to the right of the person eating pomegranate##5
25. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere between the person eating artichoke and the person traveling to rome##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2      |   3    |      4       |   5    |     6     |      7      |
| Food    | garlic     | pomegranate | kale   | apple        | orange | artichoke | strawberry  |
| City   | london | rome     | hannover | paris | san-francisco | new-york     | colone |

