.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-19::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: july, february, may, january, october, december, august
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: action, animation, comedy, epic, family, martial-arts, romance
 1. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is not the person watching animation movies##6
 3. the person who's birthday is in december is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is not to the right of the person watching action movies##8
 6. the person watching epic movies is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##8
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##8
 8. the person watching epic movies is not to the right of the person watching romance movies##8
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the left of the person watching animation movies##5
10. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who's birthday is in january##1
11. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
12. the person watching family movies is on the far left##1
13. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
14. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching romance movies##5
15. the person who's birthday is in may is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##8
16. the person watching epic movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
17. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
18. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5
19. the person who's birthday is in august is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |     4      |      5      |     6      |      7       |
| Birthday         | july | august | october | may | december | january | february      |
| Movie-Genre   | family | comedy  | epic   | romance    | action      | animation  | martial-arts |

