.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-20::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite, tea, hot-chocolate, lemonade, cola, fanta
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, lacrosse, parkour, rugby, skiing, swimming, tennis
 1. the person who's sport is parkour is not the person drinking cola##6
 2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
 4. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##5
 5. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's sport is tennis is not the person drinking juice##6
 7. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 8. the person who's sport is skiing is the person drinking fanta##1
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is the person drinking sprite##1
10. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
11. the person drinking juice is not to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
12. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
13. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
14. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
15. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##8
16. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
17. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
18. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
19. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##8
20. the person drinking lemonade is not to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2     |      3      |    4    |       5       |    6     |    7     |
| Beverage   | fanta | tea   | sprite | cola | lemonade | hot-chocolate  | juice  |
| Sport   | skiing    | badminton | parkour     | tennis  | rugby         | swimming | lacrosse |

 